        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "It has been requested that Zend_Pdf be able to operate with encrypted documents.\r\n\r\nFrom the original Trac issue (TRAC-46):\r\n{quote}\r\nHello,\r\n\r\nIs it \/ will it be possible to sign PDFs with Zend_Pdf?\r\n\r\nFor use with these kinds of files:\r\n\r\nallcert.crt (TRUSTED CERTIFICATE)\r\n\r\nprivate.pem (RSA PRIVATE KEY)\r\n\r\nrootcert.crt (A-CERT ADVANCED Selfsigned Zertifikat)\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\n\r\nPhilipp\r\n{quote}"
